query:
/*+ NoNestLoop(i ss dd) */ select dd.d_year,
i.i_category_id,
i.i_category,
sum(ss.ss_ext_sales_price)
from item AS i
inner join store_sales AS ss
on ss.ss_item_sk = i.i_item_sk AND i.i_manager_id = 1
inner join date_dim AS dd
on dd.d_date_sk = ss.ss_sold_date_sk AND dd.d_moy = 11 AND dd.d_year = 1998 group by dd.d_year, i.i_category_id, i.i_category order by sum(ss.ss_ext_sales_price) desc, dd.d_year, i.i_category_id, i.i_category LIMIT 100;
